1
00:01:33,360 --> 00:01:34,940
[OVERDO]

2
00:01:35,220 --> 00:01:37,820
[Episode 11]

3
00:02:47,870 --> 00:02:48,840
Why are you here?

4
00:02:52,490 --> 00:02:54,690
This is a photo of your adoptive mother.

5
00:02:55,310 --> 00:02:56,470
Why burn it?

6
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:05,320
She was trapped
in the Li family her whole life.

7
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:06,450
Now that she’s gone,

8
00:03:07,730 --> 00:03:08,800
I couldn’t let her

9
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:11,280
stay trapped in the Li family’s shadow.

10
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,400
Then why not keep it?

11
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:18,960
I’m not her real child.

12
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:23,000
What about Li Boze?

13
00:03:23,230 --> 00:03:24,890
Li Boze deserves it even less.

14
00:03:27,710 --> 00:03:29,250
Was your adoptive mother...

15
00:03:29,250 --> 00:03:30,400
good to you?

16
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,360
On the contrary.

17
00:03:39,630 --> 00:03:41,090
She treated me very badly.

18
00:03:42,430 --> 00:03:43,650
After taking the wrong child,

19
00:03:43,650 --> 00:03:45,590
the older I got,
the less I looked like Li Rongzhang.

20
00:03:45,590 --> 00:03:47,120
I was considered a bastard.

21
00:03:47,190 --> 00:03:48,850
She couldn't defend herself.

22
00:03:49,630 --> 00:03:50,630
Driven crazy by

23
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,640
Li Rongzhang's torment,

24
00:03:54,100 --> 00:03:56,160
she took all her resentment out on me.

25
00:03:57,100 --> 00:03:58,630
But she was also the only one

26
00:03:59,470 --> 00:04:00,360
who, when I was beaten

27
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,020
unconscious by Li Rongzhang,

28
00:04:03,190 --> 00:04:05,120
would apply medicine to my wounds.

29
00:04:18,630 --> 00:04:19,430
Do you know

30
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:23,220
why Li Rongzhang made me eat raw meat?

31
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:26,830
Why?

32
00:04:34,159 --> 00:04:35,420
It was also a rainy day.

33
00:04:36,630 --> 00:04:38,890
My adoptive mother had just passed away.

34
00:04:39,070 --> 00:04:40,750
I was all alone in the huge Li residence,

35
00:04:40,750 --> 00:04:41,950
feeling very lonely.

36
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,750
By coincidence, I found

37
00:04:43,750 --> 00:04:45,409
a stray puppy in the backyard.

38
00:04:46,430 --> 00:04:47,240
I felt

39
00:04:47,950 --> 00:04:49,070
it was just like me

40
00:04:50,070 --> 00:04:51,330
and wanted to adopt it.

41
00:04:53,630 --> 00:04:54,760
Little did I know...

42
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:01,480
Father.

43
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,300
Where did you get that?

44
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,650
Give it to me.

45
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:10,000
No.

46
00:05:10,510 --> 00:05:11,240
Give it to me!

47
00:05:11,310 --> 00:05:11,830
No!

48
00:05:24,070 --> 00:05:25,070
Lock him up.

49
00:05:25,630 --> 00:05:26,950
Don't give him any food.

50
00:05:26,950 --> 00:05:28,160
Give me back my dog!

51
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:29,830
Give it back!

52
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:30,800
I found it in the backyard!

53
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,070
Give it back to me!

54
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:32,310
Just like that,

55
00:06:33,420 --> 00:06:34,750
he starved me for 3 days.

56
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:39,380
Three days later,
that door finally opened.

57
00:06:44,970 --> 00:06:46,970
My expression when I saw the raw meat

58
00:06:47,420 --> 00:06:49,280
was exactly the same as yours now.

59
00:06:59,430 --> 00:07:01,030
This was the way Li Rongzhang

60
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:03,580
wanted to teach me to survive.

61
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:06,050
In the face of survival,

62
00:07:06,510 --> 00:07:07,770
nothing else matters.

63
00:07:10,190 --> 00:07:12,390
I was taught this way
by him for 12 years.

64
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:27,910
You don't need to pity me.

65
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,000
I just can't control

66
00:07:31,110 --> 00:07:33,310
my body's instinctive reaction to him.

67
00:07:33,900 --> 00:07:34,720
But at least

68
00:07:35,150 --> 00:07:36,560
I can resist the fear.

69
00:07:38,190 --> 00:07:39,850
Isn't it starting to work now?

70
00:07:42,900 --> 00:07:43,850
It's not pity.

71
00:07:46,580 --> 00:07:47,840
I just understand you.

72
00:07:49,890 --> 00:07:51,120
He destroyed you,

73
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,060
but he also molded you.

74
00:07:54,380 --> 00:07:56,240
In front of its creator,

75
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:58,159
a piece of work

76
00:08:00,390 --> 00:08:01,790
is utterly defenseless.

77
00:08:05,750 --> 00:08:06,560
Yes.

78
00:08:07,390 --> 00:08:08,190
You are right.

79
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,160
He is a monster.

80
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,680
Raised by him,

81
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,680
I am a monster too.

82
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:23,750
That's why

83
00:08:24,310 --> 00:08:25,360
three years ago,

84
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:28,330
I could sense
something fishy in your letter.

85
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,390
You and I

86
00:08:29,630 --> 00:08:31,890
are essentially the same kind of people.

87
00:08:33,850 --> 00:08:35,480
Maybe what you are doing now

88
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,630
has something to do

89
00:08:37,909 --> 00:08:39,240
with Xiaolan back then.

90
00:08:45,390 --> 00:08:46,990
It has nothing to do with you.

91
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:48,720
Ren Susu,

92
00:08:49,390 --> 00:08:52,320
no one in this world
understands you better than I do.

93
00:08:53,870 --> 00:08:55,400
You can tell me everything.

94
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:58,100
Having an ally
is better than fighting alone.

95
00:08:58,100 --> 00:08:59,240
I don't need allies.

96
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:02,670
Alright.

97
00:09:02,910 --> 00:09:03,600
Fine.

98
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,640
Since we can't be allies,

99
00:09:06,510 --> 00:09:07,720
then I must warn you.

100
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,360
Turn yourself in,

101
00:09:09,510 --> 00:09:11,150
or leave Murong Qingyu.

102
00:09:13,870 --> 00:09:14,670
Otherwise,

103
00:09:15,870 --> 00:09:17,600
you'll bear the consequences.

104
00:09:19,270 --> 00:09:22,360
Have you forgotten the lesson
of the blood wedding dress already?

105
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,750
You really never learn.

106
00:09:24,780 --> 00:09:25,850
I'll say it again—

107
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:28,440
mind your own business.

108
00:09:33,670 --> 00:09:34,870
Mind my own business?

109
00:09:37,910 --> 00:09:39,310
At the Li family just now,

110
00:09:40,550 --> 00:09:42,150
who was minding my business?

111
00:09:46,910 --> 00:09:48,240
You helped me last time,

112
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:51,730
so I was returning the favor this time.

113
00:09:59,050 --> 00:10:00,690
♪ In exchange for my everything ♪

114
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:03,030
♪ Will you finally be mine? ♪

115
00:10:03,710 --> 00:10:05,650
♪ Give me love and hate ♪

116
00:10:05,670 --> 00:10:08,520
♪ I can't break free, I can't escape ♪

117
00:10:09,050 --> 00:10:11,400
♪ This, too, can be called
a lifetime together ♪

118
00:10:11,430 --> 00:10:12,800
♪ We ♪

119
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,860
♪ Remain bound by fate until the end ♪

120
00:10:16,490 --> 00:10:23,160
♪ Forevermore ♪

121
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,060
Young Master Boze.

122
00:10:35,270 --> 00:10:36,930
Be careful not to catch a cold.

123
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,200
I'm fine.

124
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:39,670
Is Qingyi back?

125
00:10:39,670 --> 00:10:40,320
Dudu?

126
00:10:41,510 --> 00:10:44,170
Why did you come over
in the rain so late at night?

127
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,120
Mother.

128
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:47,790
Look at you.

129
00:10:48,030 --> 00:10:49,120
You're soaked.

130
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,440
Hurry up and prepare

131
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,080
a set of dry clothes
for Young Master Boze.

132
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:52,630
Also,

133
00:10:52,630 --> 00:10:53,200
make some ginger soup.

134
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,080
I'll go right away.

135
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:54,630
Come.

136
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:03,220
You don't need to worry about him.

137
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,480
He's used to being free.

138
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:06,240
Who knows if he'll come back.

139
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,030
Mother,

140
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:12,840
do you know

141
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:15,740
what happened to Qingyi at the Li family?

142
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,030
Li Rongzhang

143
00:11:24,670 --> 00:11:27,130
always thought Qingyi
didn't look like him,

144
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:30,270
so he suspected your biological mother

145
00:11:30,270 --> 00:11:31,320
of infidelity.

146
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:33,930
He thought Qingyi was a bastard

147
00:11:34,940 --> 00:11:36,340
and beat him frequently.

148
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:39,790
Later, we found out

149
00:11:39,790 --> 00:11:42,190
that the 2 families had mixed up
our babies.

150
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,480
You were still young then,

151
00:11:47,870 --> 00:11:50,130
and I couldn't bear to just send you back.

152
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,390
So you and Qingyi

153
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:56,380
weren't switched back immediately.

154
00:11:58,480 --> 00:12:00,670
But the way Li Rongzhang treated him

155
00:12:01,270 --> 00:12:02,470
couldn't be changed.

156
00:12:03,870 --> 00:12:05,470
It has always been like this.

157
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:06,260
But Mother,

158
00:12:07,790 --> 00:12:08,960
later, didn't you also...

159
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:09,820
He deserved it.

160
00:12:11,270 --> 00:12:13,070
They were torturing each other.

161
00:12:13,150 --> 00:12:14,270
Why should I care?

162
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:15,670
But Qingyi is your biological son.

163
00:12:15,670 --> 00:12:16,390
Back then,

164
00:12:17,790 --> 00:12:19,550
he clearly heard

165
00:12:19,630 --> 00:12:21,270
the news that Li Rongzhang
was going to assassinate your father,

166
00:12:21,270 --> 00:12:23,150
but he failed to explain it clearly.

167
00:12:23,150 --> 00:12:25,320
And that caused your father's death!

168
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:28,840
After your father died,

169
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:31,900
he woke up and shouted, "Watch out!"
What was the point?

170
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:37,240
Mother.

171
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:46,760
The incident 12 years ago

172
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:50,730
was not caused by my father
from the Li family.

173
00:12:51,390 --> 00:12:53,250
Qingyi was too young at that time,

174
00:12:53,750 --> 00:12:56,150
and he didn't see
who was behind it clearly.

175
00:12:57,630 --> 00:12:59,120
So there is no evidence for this.

176
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:00,720
Even if there's no evidence,

177
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,200
he had a motive.

178
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:07,600
Alright.

179
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:11,170
It's raining heavily outside,

180
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:12,600
so don't go back today.

181
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,240
Finish the ginger soup

182
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:15,240
and go take a rest.

183
00:13:17,550 --> 00:13:18,150
Okay.

184
00:13:25,570 --> 00:13:28,270
[Zarry Grand Hotel]

185
00:13:26,870 --> 00:13:28,130
Boss Hai, you're here.

186
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:29,100
Please come in.

187
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:31,130
We've saved a table for you.

188
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,510
These wealthy families

189
00:13:36,150 --> 00:13:38,350
have been shocking me every single day.

190
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:41,000
Could it be

191
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,980
that Li Boze did it on purpose?

192
00:13:44,150 --> 00:13:46,840
He knows the relationship between
Li Rongzhang and Murong Qingyi,

193
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:48,440
so he intentionally intensified
the conflict.

194
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:49,300
It couldn't be.

195
00:13:50,510 --> 00:13:51,840
With his simple mind,

196
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:53,370
he couldn't do such a thing.

197
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:58,120
You've only met him a few times,

198
00:13:58,120 --> 00:14:00,050
but you seem to know him quite well.

199
00:14:00,390 --> 00:14:01,750
Life is like a play.

200
00:14:01,870 --> 00:14:04,930
I've played so many roles
and sung about so many hearts.

201
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:07,910
A young master like Li Boze,
who can be seen through at a glance,

202
00:14:07,910 --> 00:14:09,170
is the easiest to read.

203
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:13,870
But I must remind you.

204
00:14:14,550 --> 00:14:16,390
Both of them are sons of the two families,

205
00:14:16,390 --> 00:14:17,720
but Murong Qingyi's thoughts

206
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:20,270
are so deep
that they can't be seen through.

207
00:14:20,630 --> 00:14:21,840
You chased after him to the Li family

208
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:24,170
probably out of pity for him again, right?

209
00:14:29,270 --> 00:14:31,800
I just didn't want to drag him
into this again.

210
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:33,630
What if he reveals your identity

211
00:14:33,630 --> 00:14:34,960
to Murong Qingyu?

212
00:14:36,670 --> 00:14:37,440
Don't worry.

213
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:39,030
I am prepared.

214
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:47,550
Tao?

215
00:14:47,790 --> 00:14:48,720
Why are you here?

216
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,480
He has been looking for you.

217
00:14:50,480 --> 00:14:51,630
I was afraid of arousing suspicion,

218
00:14:51,630 --> 00:14:53,090
so I just let him come here.

219
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:54,200
Don't worry, Sister.

220
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:55,200
We older kids

221
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:57,510
are usually sent out
to beg during the day.

222
00:14:57,510 --> 00:14:58,670
No one is watching us these days,

223
00:14:58,670 --> 00:14:59,930
so no one will find out.

224
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:02,550
Eat up.

225
00:15:06,750 --> 00:15:08,210
Why are you looking for us?

226
00:15:09,630 --> 00:15:11,960
The orphanage is sending out goods again.

227
00:15:13,840 --> 00:15:14,720
At a time like this,

228
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:16,180
they still dare to do this?

229
00:15:16,790 --> 00:15:18,270
There's only what you can't imagine,

230
00:15:18,270 --> 00:15:20,130
nothing they wouldn't dare to do.

231
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:22,260
What kind of goods?

232
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:23,870
Pretty girls.

233
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:25,960
Those people dress them in skirts

234
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:28,760
and lock them in the building of the new orphanage.

235
00:15:28,870 --> 00:15:30,080
It's the premium goods

236
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:32,610
whose whereabouts
we could never track down.

237
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:34,060
Over the years,

238
00:15:34,390 --> 00:15:35,960
the girls who were sold to rich families

239
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:37,270
and brothels

240
00:15:37,630 --> 00:15:39,290
could always be tracked down.

241
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:41,080
But the most beautiful girls

242
00:15:41,200 --> 00:15:42,670
have completely disappeared.

243
00:15:42,670 --> 00:15:43,870
We've been investigating for so long,

244
00:15:43,870 --> 00:15:44,750
and we still don't even know

245
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:46,350
where their black market is.

246
00:15:51,080 --> 00:15:53,140
Last time, because of Murong Qingyi,

247
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:55,130
I failed to get information

248
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:57,560
about the Elite Club from Li Rongzhang.

249
00:15:57,910 --> 00:15:59,240
You suspect this club

250
00:15:59,240 --> 00:16:01,500
is related to the Huo family's business?

251
00:16:01,750 --> 00:16:03,200
This Elite Club

252
00:16:03,200 --> 00:16:05,320
is single-handedly run by the Huo family.

253
00:16:05,320 --> 00:16:06,960
The entry requirements are strict,

254
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:08,550
and the information
is strictly confidential.

255
00:16:08,550 --> 00:16:10,320
With a fixed buyer group

256
00:16:10,630 --> 00:16:12,550
and confidential trading channels,

257
00:16:12,550 --> 00:16:13,480
what do you think

258
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:16,150
they are trading?

259
00:16:26,030 --> 00:16:26,790
Tao,

260
00:16:27,480 --> 00:16:28,410
here. Take this.

261
00:16:29,320 --> 00:16:31,450
Take this as what you begged for today.

262
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:32,600
From now on,

263
00:16:32,790 --> 00:16:34,720
we should not contact each other anymore.

264
00:16:34,720 --> 00:16:35,960
Even if you get news,

265
00:16:36,240 --> 00:16:37,790
don't rush to find us.

266
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:39,000
Protect yourself.

267
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:39,730
Understand?

268
00:16:40,510 --> 00:16:41,120
Yes.

269
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:42,120
Thank you, Sister.

270
00:16:42,120 --> 00:16:42,790
Go now.

271
00:16:44,270 --> 00:16:45,330
Goodbye, Sisters.

272
00:16:49,750 --> 00:16:51,390
This child is quite clever.

273
00:16:53,200 --> 00:16:54,400
What should we do now?

274
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:57,620
It's an eventful time.

275
00:16:57,870 --> 00:17:00,600
These girls from the orphanage
won't be locked up for long.

276
00:17:00,600 --> 00:17:01,600
Notify the sisters

277
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:03,270
to keep a close eye on the orphanage.

278
00:17:03,270 --> 00:17:04,680
I will try to find another way

279
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:05,940
through the Li family.

280
00:17:11,720 --> 00:17:13,400
With something like this happening,

281
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:15,660
the police station cannot escape blame.

282
00:17:16,270 --> 00:17:18,829
The police station is going through
a leadership transition right now.

283
00:17:18,829 --> 00:17:20,560
The Huo family has a say in this.

284
00:17:22,550 --> 00:17:25,609
Inspector Li has already sent someone
to investigate.

285
00:17:26,270 --> 00:17:27,270
Young Master Huo.

286
00:17:27,270 --> 00:17:29,030
This little girl
was also there that night.

287
00:17:29,030 --> 00:17:31,160
She stopped me
and insisted on singing for me.

288
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:32,110
Let me ask you,

289
00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:33,920
where did Nanny Sun go

290
00:17:34,270 --> 00:17:35,110
that night?

291
00:17:36,240 --> 00:17:38,680
Nanny Sun ran off with a man.

292
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:40,720
These brats!

293
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:41,920
Why so fierce?

294
00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:43,740
Can't you talk nicely?

295
00:17:53,070 --> 00:17:54,240
Is this your doll?

296
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:56,030
It's so cute.

297
00:17:57,400 --> 00:17:58,480
Tell me,

298
00:17:59,110 --> 00:18:01,400
why did you sing for them that night?

299
00:18:01,790 --> 00:18:03,880
Nanny told us to practice singing.

300
00:18:06,110 --> 00:18:07,920
Then when did Nanny

301
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:09,580
have you practice in the yard?

302
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:11,680
Right...

303
00:18:11,680 --> 00:18:13,440
Right before bedtime.

304
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:18,310
I want to hear it too.

305
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:21,070
Can you sing it for me?

306
00:18:44,440 --> 00:18:45,160
Wait!

307
00:18:46,240 --> 00:18:47,030
Well...

308
00:18:47,110 --> 00:18:47,590
You!

309
00:18:48,480 --> 00:18:49,810
-Come here.
-Come here!

310
00:18:50,590 --> 00:18:52,390
Do you know where Nanny Sun went?

311
00:18:54,270 --> 00:18:54,960
I know.

312
00:18:55,070 --> 00:18:56,510
Nanny Sun ran off with a man.

313
00:18:56,510 --> 00:18:57,350
Who said that?

314
00:18:58,310 --> 00:18:59,350
The janitor,

315
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:00,880
the plump auntie,

316
00:19:00,880 --> 00:19:02,270
and Sister He from the senior class.

317
00:19:02,270 --> 00:19:03,310
They all said so.

318
00:19:04,110 --> 00:19:06,110
Those gossiping busybodies.

319
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:07,030
Go!

320
00:19:38,070 --> 00:19:38,960
It's sweet?

321
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:42,790
Did you see?

322
00:19:43,110 --> 00:19:44,110
Young Master Qingyu and Miss Fang's

323
00:19:44,110 --> 00:19:45,640
wedding outfits have arrived.

324
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:47,480
I heard they were made
by a foreign tailor.

325
00:19:47,480 --> 00:19:48,740
They're magnificent.

326
00:19:58,720 --> 00:20:00,180
Are your injuries better?

327
00:20:02,160 --> 00:20:03,270
I won't die.

328
00:20:04,110 --> 00:20:05,570
Have you made up your mind?

329
00:20:07,200 --> 00:20:08,000
About what?

330
00:20:10,030 --> 00:20:11,590
The two choices I gave you.

331
00:20:17,350 --> 00:20:18,110
Miss Fang,

332
00:20:18,200 --> 00:20:20,660
where do you want to try on
the wedding dress?

333
00:20:23,200 --> 00:20:24,400
I'll do it right here.

334
00:20:26,350 --> 00:20:28,350
Go to the study and call Qingyu over.

335
00:20:29,480 --> 00:20:30,240
Yes.

336
00:20:36,960 --> 00:20:38,000
Try it on here?

337
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:40,680
Aren't you afraid

338
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:42,160
I'll expose you here?

339
00:20:43,920 --> 00:20:44,750
Just try it.

340
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:52,400
Very good.

341
00:20:58,880 --> 00:20:59,550
Qingyu.

342
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:03,000
Mother.

343
00:21:04,590 --> 00:21:05,830
Is this your wedding outfit?

344
00:21:05,830 --> 00:21:06,590
It looks...

345
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:08,370
like it doesn't quite fit.

346
00:21:08,370 --> 00:21:09,680
This outfit is so important.

347
00:21:09,680 --> 00:21:11,140
Why isn't it finished yet?

348
00:21:11,510 --> 00:21:13,200
Qingyu had an emergency that day.

349
00:21:13,200 --> 00:21:15,000
Qingyi tried on the suit for him.

350
00:21:17,480 --> 00:21:18,960
They have different builds.

351
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:21,680
How could the tailor
get the measurements right?

352
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:23,210
All he does is make trouble.

353
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:25,070
Qingyi was just trying to help me.

354
00:21:25,070 --> 00:21:26,590
It's not his fault.

355
00:21:29,400 --> 00:21:32,000
Miss Fang,
have you chosen your wedding dress?

356
00:21:33,310 --> 00:21:34,880
The wedding dress I originally chose

357
00:21:34,880 --> 00:21:36,210
was replaced by Qingyi.

358
00:21:37,920 --> 00:21:38,960
Was there something wrong

359
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:40,820
with the original wedding dress?

360
00:21:42,590 --> 00:21:44,450
The original dress was too plain.

361
00:21:45,720 --> 00:21:47,160
It didn't suit Miss Fang's

362
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:48,350
bootlicker vibe.

363
00:21:50,680 --> 00:21:51,350
Qingyi.

364
00:21:56,270 --> 00:21:57,870
Qingyi is just envious of us.

365
00:21:58,000 --> 00:21:59,350
After we get married,

366
00:21:59,590 --> 00:22:00,960
I'll help Mother

367
00:22:01,680 --> 00:22:04,140
arrange the wedding
for Qingyi and Miss Huo.

368
00:22:05,030 --> 00:22:06,480
Who said I'm going to marry Huo Minxian?

369
00:22:06,480 --> 00:22:08,740
Marriage is a serious matter, not a joke.

370
00:22:09,350 --> 00:22:10,000
It's fine.

371
00:22:10,480 --> 00:22:12,680
If Qingyi really doesn't like Miss Huo,

372
00:22:13,480 --> 00:22:14,920
as his sister-in-law,

373
00:22:15,240 --> 00:22:16,790
I'll help him look for a suitable match

374
00:22:16,790 --> 00:22:18,000
among the noble ladies in Nancheng.

375
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:20,260
He'll definitely find someone he likes.

376
00:22:21,070 --> 00:22:21,750
Yeah.

377
00:22:22,480 --> 00:22:25,410
Sister-in-law and Qingyu
are getting married soon.

378
00:22:25,960 --> 00:22:27,070
It's a pity that Qingyu

379
00:22:27,070 --> 00:22:29,200
still hasn't seen
her true colors.

380
00:22:33,070 --> 00:22:34,350
What nonsense are you talking about?

381
00:22:34,350 --> 00:22:35,410
How is it nonsense?

382
00:22:35,920 --> 00:22:37,030
She's not Fang...

383
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:42,920
Why is this dress torn?

384
00:22:43,350 --> 00:22:45,550
It was perfectly fine when we packed it.

385
00:22:49,590 --> 00:22:50,720
Who else could it be?

386
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:53,680
Let me see.

387
00:22:56,440 --> 00:22:57,770
Why is it torn like this?

388
00:22:59,270 --> 00:22:59,960
It's fine.

389
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:00,920
Mother,

390
00:23:01,310 --> 00:23:03,510
we can have another wedding dress made.

391
00:23:09,590 --> 00:23:10,650
You suspect me too?

392
00:23:13,200 --> 00:23:15,130
Apologize to your sister-in-law.

393
00:23:21,920 --> 00:23:22,960
What if I don't?

394
00:23:23,270 --> 00:23:24,880
Are you going to kill me today?

395
00:23:24,880 --> 00:23:25,720
Did you do nothing wrong?

396
00:23:25,720 --> 00:23:26,750
Whether I was wrong or not,

397
00:23:26,750 --> 00:23:28,750
didn't you already send me to prison
3 years ago?

398
00:23:28,750 --> 00:23:29,480
Qingyi,

399
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:31,070
these are two different matters.

400
00:23:31,070 --> 00:23:32,880
I personally witnessed several times

401
00:23:32,880 --> 00:23:34,350
that you targeted your sister-in-law.

402
00:23:34,350 --> 00:23:36,030
It doesn't matter
if you have a problem with me.

403
00:23:36,030 --> 00:23:37,070
If you want to vent your anger,

404
00:23:37,070 --> 00:23:39,130
don't take it out on innocent people.

405
00:23:41,270 --> 00:23:42,400
Innocent people?

406
00:23:44,590 --> 00:23:45,750
She's innocent?

407
00:23:54,270 --> 00:23:54,960
Fine.

408
00:23:56,160 --> 00:23:57,160
Everyone is innocent.

409
00:23:57,160 --> 00:23:58,310
I'm the only one who was born a bad seed!

410
00:23:58,310 --> 00:23:59,480
I'm the shame of the Murong family!

411
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:00,200
Are you happy now?

412
00:24:00,200 --> 00:24:01,000
No one said that.

413
00:24:01,000 --> 00:24:02,330
But that's what you did.

414
00:24:08,400 --> 00:24:10,260
You didn't believe me 3 years ago,

415
00:24:10,350 --> 00:24:12,280
and you still don't believe me now.

416
00:24:12,480 --> 00:24:14,160
Do you deserve to be my older brother?

417
00:24:14,160 --> 00:24:14,920
Shut up!

418
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:18,920
Is that how you talk to your brother?

419
00:24:18,920 --> 00:24:20,180
Since you were a child,

420
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:22,270
Qingyu has always been
cleaning up your messes.

421
00:24:22,270 --> 00:24:23,400
If it weren't for him,

422
00:24:23,400 --> 00:24:24,680
would you even have a place
in the Murong family?

423
00:24:24,680 --> 00:24:26,550
Is the Murong family anything good?

424
00:24:26,550 --> 00:24:28,480
Do you really think I want to be a Mu—

425
00:24:29,480 --> 00:24:30,000
Get out!

426
00:24:42,070 --> 00:24:43,000
Bastard!

427
00:24:45,160 --> 00:24:46,560
Hurry up and take it back.

428
00:24:47,440 --> 00:24:48,110
Miss Fang,

429
00:24:49,480 --> 00:24:51,280
hurry up and choose another one.

430
00:25:01,400 --> 00:25:02,480
On behalf of Qingyi,

431
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:03,680
I apologize to you.

432
00:25:04,270 --> 00:25:05,590
He is a bit hot-tempered,

433
00:25:05,590 --> 00:25:06,720
but he means no harm.

434
00:25:07,880 --> 00:25:09,340
Maybe he feels that lately

435
00:25:09,350 --> 00:25:11,110
you've taken away my attention,

436
00:25:11,110 --> 00:25:13,170
so he's throwing a childish tantrum.

437
00:25:17,790 --> 00:25:18,480
Perhaps.

438
00:25:20,510 --> 00:25:22,840
People of the Murong family, get out here!

439
00:25:32,150 --> 00:25:33,480
Your Murong family

440
00:25:34,030 --> 00:25:36,070
is truly shameless.

441
00:25:38,000 --> 00:25:38,790
Marshal Li.

442
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:41,510
Back then, Peilin supported you,

443
00:25:41,510 --> 00:25:43,550
who came from a humble background.

444
00:25:44,550 --> 00:25:46,480
You were so attentive at that time.

445
00:25:47,880 --> 00:25:49,030
Now that Peilin

446
00:25:49,550 --> 00:25:50,680
is dead

447
00:25:51,640 --> 00:25:53,700
and the real killer is still at large,

448
00:25:54,070 --> 00:25:56,640
you dare to throw your weight around
in the Murong family?

449
00:25:56,640 --> 00:25:59,970
Do you really think there's no one left
in the Murong family?

450
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:01,930
Even if there is, they are useless.

451
00:26:04,720 --> 00:26:05,480
Uncle Li,

452
00:26:06,400 --> 00:26:08,000
please make yourself clear.

453
00:26:08,200 --> 00:26:09,400
What exactly is this?

454
00:26:16,110 --> 00:26:18,960
Murong Qingyi was abused by those bastards

455
00:26:19,960 --> 00:26:21,620
from the Huo family for 3 years

456
00:26:21,960 --> 00:26:24,220
and had the tendons in his hands severed.

457
00:26:39,790 --> 00:26:41,350
So you experienced

458
00:26:42,440 --> 00:26:44,000
more than what you told me.

459
00:27:00,790 --> 00:27:01,450
This was...

460
00:27:04,720 --> 00:27:06,380
This was in prison, wasn't it?

461
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:08,800
What else could it have been?

462
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:36,640
Cheng Jinzhi,

463
00:27:36,880 --> 00:27:38,480
your own son spent 3 years in prison

464
00:27:38,480 --> 00:27:40,720
being abused by the Huo family,

465
00:27:41,440 --> 00:27:43,960
and they even severed
the tendons in his hands.

466
00:27:43,960 --> 00:27:44,750
Now,

467
00:27:45,110 --> 00:27:47,790
you're letting him
be the Huo family's son-in-law?

468
00:27:47,790 --> 00:27:49,240
Your Murong family

469
00:27:49,640 --> 00:27:51,830
is truly adaptable.

470
00:27:55,440 --> 00:27:57,240
I was sold for a good price by you.

471
00:27:58,000 --> 00:28:00,130
Who's the one being embarrassed here?

472
00:28:00,720 --> 00:28:01,780
If you are unhappy,

473
00:28:02,030 --> 00:28:03,160
you might send me to prison again

474
00:28:03,160 --> 00:28:04,690
for another several years.

475
00:28:04,830 --> 00:28:06,110
I can't afford that.

476
00:28:06,680 --> 00:28:07,480
Family?

477
00:28:08,640 --> 00:28:09,570
Is this a family?

478
00:28:15,400 --> 00:28:17,690
Your Murong family
might be able to swallow this,

479
00:28:17,690 --> 00:28:18,440
[According to the Huo family's order,
we followed Mao to the prison.]

480
00:28:17,920 --> 00:28:19,000
but I can't.

481
00:28:18,460 --> 00:28:19,460
[While Murong Qingyi was defenseless,
I held down his head]

482
00:28:19,490 --> 00:28:20,710
[and shoulders, and Mao severed...]

483
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:21,780
I was fighting on the front lines.

484
00:28:22,440 --> 00:28:25,370
How dare the Huo family
secretly plot against my man?

485
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:26,970
Regarding this matter,

486
00:28:27,270 --> 00:28:29,000
he killed someone first.

487
00:28:29,240 --> 00:28:31,510
It was understandable
for the Huo family to vent their anger.

488
00:28:31,510 --> 00:28:32,510
Understandable?

489
00:28:32,550 --> 00:28:34,880
Your Murong family is prestigious,

490
00:28:35,030 --> 00:28:38,480
yet you let the Huo family
mess with him in prison.

491
00:28:39,350 --> 00:28:41,030
When I sent this kid back,

492
00:28:41,030 --> 00:28:42,680
he was in one piece.

493
00:28:42,680 --> 00:28:43,590
Twelve years.

494
00:28:43,920 --> 00:28:45,110
In just 12 years,

495
00:28:45,240 --> 00:28:47,700
he was labeled a killer,
served prison time,

496
00:28:47,880 --> 00:28:49,680
and had his tendons severed.

497
00:28:49,960 --> 00:28:52,160
Who else should I blame but your family?

498
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:57,680
Qingyu!

499
00:28:58,440 --> 00:28:59,570
Where are you going?

500
00:29:03,880 --> 00:29:05,280
What exactly do you want?

501
00:29:06,920 --> 00:29:07,850
I'm telling you,

502
00:29:08,310 --> 00:29:10,590
you must give me an explanation today.

503
00:29:11,550 --> 00:29:13,000
A member of our Murong family

504
00:29:13,000 --> 00:29:14,460
was hurt by the Huo family.

505
00:29:14,880 --> 00:29:17,200
Why should we give the Li family
an explanation?

506
00:29:17,200 --> 00:29:19,800
You should know whose toes
you're stepping on.

507
00:29:20,350 --> 00:29:21,310
If word gets out,

508
00:29:21,400 --> 00:29:22,790
people will think the Huo family

509
00:29:22,790 --> 00:29:24,880
dares to walk all over me.

510
00:29:25,240 --> 00:29:26,550
I would lose face.

511
00:29:27,720 --> 00:29:29,250
Let me tell you this, Cheng.

512
00:29:32,640 --> 00:29:34,570
Give me 200 boxes of rifle bullets,

513
00:29:35,240 --> 00:29:36,550
and I'll let this go.

514
00:29:45,200 --> 00:29:46,680
So, Marshal Li,

515
00:29:47,440 --> 00:29:49,510
after all that talk about justice,

516
00:29:50,400 --> 00:29:52,530
you are actually here to blackmail us?

517
00:29:53,310 --> 00:29:54,000
Servants.

518
00:29:54,030 --> 00:29:55,030
See the guest out!

519
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:58,200
I don't mind if this ends up
in the newspapers tomorrow

520
00:29:58,350 --> 00:30:00,110
and everyone in Nancheng finds out

521
00:30:00,110 --> 00:30:02,590
that the Murong family
got their youngest son crippled

522
00:30:02,590 --> 00:30:04,400
and forced him to marry their enemy,

523
00:30:04,400 --> 00:30:07,060
all just to get some planes
for their eldest son.

524
00:30:11,110 --> 00:30:13,440
If this problem can be solved
with 200 boxes of rifle bullets,

525
00:30:13,440 --> 00:30:15,160
you should...

526
00:30:15,400 --> 00:30:16,230
think twice.

527
00:30:35,170 --> 00:30:36,500
[Renxin Orphanage]

528
00:31:03,110 --> 00:31:04,480
Let's go! Stop unloading the goods!

529
00:31:04,480 --> 00:31:05,340
Let's go drink!

530
00:31:05,400 --> 00:31:06,600
-Let’s go.
-Let’s go.

531
00:31:29,110 --> 00:31:30,920
This is a girl's hair?

532
00:31:40,880 --> 00:31:41,510
Boss Hai.

533
00:31:53,310 --> 00:31:55,590
Inspector Li,
you and I are really destined.

534
00:31:55,590 --> 00:31:56,240
How come

535
00:31:56,350 --> 00:31:57,920
we meet in a slum

536
00:31:57,920 --> 00:31:58,750
like this?

537
00:31:59,700 --> 00:32:01,720
So Boss Hai, you know this is a slum?

538
00:32:02,110 --> 00:32:03,310
Then why are you here?

539
00:32:04,150 --> 00:32:06,110
You are so bossy, Inspector Li.

540
00:32:06,310 --> 00:32:08,310
If you can come, why can't I?

541
00:32:08,720 --> 00:32:10,450
I'm here to investigate a case.

542
00:32:10,720 --> 00:32:11,680
What case?

543
00:32:13,680 --> 00:32:14,400
Boss Hai,

544
00:32:14,880 --> 00:32:16,810
are you interrogating the police?

545
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:19,720
Then what do you want to ask me?

546
00:32:20,030 --> 00:32:22,490
Nanny Sun from Renxin Orphanage
is missing.

547
00:32:22,510 --> 00:32:23,240
Do you know

548
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:24,160
about this?

549
00:32:28,070 --> 00:32:29,000
I don't know her.

550
00:32:29,590 --> 00:32:30,240
And I don't know about this.

551
00:32:30,240 --> 00:32:30,790
Really?

552
00:32:32,240 --> 00:32:34,000
I heard that whenever
Nanny Sun from Renxin Orphanage

553
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:35,200
returns to Nancheng,

554
00:32:35,240 --> 00:32:37,500
she goes to Dongjiadu to do charity work.

555
00:32:37,510 --> 00:32:38,710
And coincidentally,

556
00:32:38,790 --> 00:32:40,590
you were seen at both
the aviation school's opening ceremony

557
00:32:40,590 --> 00:32:41,320
she attended

558
00:32:41,400 --> 00:32:42,350
and Dongjiadu.

559
00:32:43,440 --> 00:32:44,070
Boss Hai,

560
00:32:45,070 --> 00:32:47,000
isn't this a bit too coincidental?

561
00:32:50,240 --> 00:32:52,500
Do you solve cases based on coincidence?

562
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:55,350
No wonder the case clearance rate
goes up so quickly.

563
00:32:55,350 --> 00:32:57,010
I often come here to volunteer

564
00:32:57,070 --> 00:32:58,670
and help some poor children.

565
00:33:02,270 --> 00:33:04,030
So you have such a kind heart.

566
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:08,730
I was born into poverty.

567
00:33:08,960 --> 00:33:11,400
I owe everything I have today
to the support of my fans.

568
00:33:11,400 --> 00:33:13,030
Naturally,
I can't forget where I came from.

569
00:33:13,030 --> 00:33:14,350
But Inspector Li,

570
00:33:14,790 --> 00:33:15,790
is everyone

571
00:33:15,790 --> 00:33:16,750
in the police station like you,

572
00:33:16,750 --> 00:33:17,960
privileged young masters
who grew up in comfort and luxury,

573
00:33:17,960 --> 00:33:20,620
never having suffered
a hard day in their lives?

574
00:33:20,790 --> 00:33:22,160
No wonder in this world,

575
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:23,590
good people receive no reward,

576
00:33:23,590 --> 00:33:25,160
and bad people face no consequences.

577
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:26,400
Watch your words, Boss Hai.

578
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:27,270
I think

579
00:33:27,550 --> 00:33:28,440
since I became a police officer,

580
00:33:28,440 --> 00:33:30,570
I haven't slacked off for a single day.

581
00:33:31,310 --> 00:33:32,440
Fools aren't scary.

582
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:35,200
What's scary are hardworking fools.

583
00:33:36,000 --> 00:33:38,070
But still, I like fools.

584
00:33:44,030 --> 00:33:45,490
Inspector Li, I advise you

585
00:33:45,510 --> 00:33:48,070
to go back to being
the wealthy young master you are.

586
00:33:48,070 --> 00:33:50,400
An upright official who speaks for the people
doesn't suit you.

587
00:33:50,400 --> 00:33:52,070
When it comes to
the suffering of the people,

588
00:33:52,070 --> 00:33:53,000
I'm afraid

589
00:33:53,270 --> 00:33:56,070
Young Master Qingyi
understands better than you.

590
00:34:19,800 --> 00:34:20,550
Have you found him?

591
00:34:20,550 --> 00:34:21,480
Where is Qingyu?

592
00:34:21,510 --> 00:34:22,630
Young Master Qingyu
searched the passenger transport,

593
00:34:22,630 --> 00:34:24,030
docks, and stations,

594
00:34:24,590 --> 00:34:25,850
but couldn't find him.

595
00:34:26,320 --> 00:34:27,840
We also checked
Young Master Qingyi's residence.

596
00:34:27,840 --> 00:34:28,969
He hasn't been back.

597
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:32,600
The rain is getting heavier.

598
00:34:32,670 --> 00:34:34,360
Tell Qingyu to come back
and wait for news.

599
00:34:34,360 --> 00:34:35,630
The rest of you can keep looking.

600
00:34:35,630 --> 00:34:36,830
Young Master refused

601
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:38,230
and asked me to report back.

602
00:34:38,230 --> 00:34:41,360
He went to Young Master Qingyi's garden
on Hongmei Road.

603
00:34:42,710 --> 00:34:43,760
Marshal Li,

604
00:34:44,320 --> 00:34:45,360
why don't you go back first?

605
00:34:45,360 --> 00:34:46,760
I've already had someone

606
00:34:46,960 --> 00:34:49,150
send the telegram
to inventory the supplies.

607
00:34:49,150 --> 00:34:51,280
Qingyi is not a three-year-old child.

608
00:34:51,360 --> 00:34:52,840
He's just temporarily out of touch.

609
00:34:52,840 --> 00:34:54,440
What's there to worry about?

610
00:34:56,590 --> 00:34:58,360
His mother isn't even worried,

611
00:34:58,800 --> 00:35:00,190
so why should others be?

612
00:35:05,360 --> 00:35:06,670
What kind of talk is that?

613
00:35:06,670 --> 00:35:07,440
Human talk.

614
00:35:24,350 --> 00:35:25,360
I'm going to pray.

615
00:35:26,230 --> 00:35:27,630
Serve tea for Marshal Li.

616
00:35:29,190 --> 00:35:30,800
Marshal Li can leave

617
00:35:31,030 --> 00:35:32,090
whenever he wants.

618
00:35:50,150 --> 00:35:51,190
Young Master Qingyi

619
00:35:51,190 --> 00:35:52,880
is quite like you, Marshal Li.

620
00:35:55,110 --> 00:35:55,840
How so?

621
00:35:56,710 --> 00:35:57,800
Unscrupulous

622
00:35:58,230 --> 00:35:59,440
and sharp-tongued.

623
00:36:01,880 --> 00:36:02,960
Now I know

624
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:05,230
who he learned it from.

625
00:36:13,190 --> 00:36:14,650
What are you trying to say?

626
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:22,480
You've already got what you wanted.

627
00:36:23,030 --> 00:36:24,760
What are you still waiting for?

628
00:36:30,670 --> 00:36:32,400
I could tell when we last met

629
00:36:33,630 --> 00:36:34,830
that you are actually

630
00:36:35,400 --> 00:36:37,060
the one who knows Qingyi best.

631
00:36:38,840 --> 00:36:39,880
You came today

632
00:36:40,630 --> 00:36:41,550
not only for

633
00:36:41,550 --> 00:36:43,410
those 200 boxes of rifle bullets,

634
00:36:44,110 --> 00:36:46,400
but also to stand up for Qingyi,

635
00:36:46,810 --> 00:36:47,510
right?

636
00:36:59,070 --> 00:37:01,270
You think you're very smart, don't you?

637
00:37:04,550 --> 00:37:06,150
People say you are

638
00:37:06,670 --> 00:37:08,070
rough and unreasonable,

639
00:37:08,960 --> 00:37:11,320
but they don't know
you are very meticulous.

640
00:37:11,320 --> 00:37:12,550
My little cleverness

641
00:37:13,000 --> 00:37:14,630
is nothing in front of you.

642
00:37:16,230 --> 00:37:18,490
But whether it is for Qingyi's grievance

643
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:20,000
or your dignity,

644
00:37:20,710 --> 00:37:21,510
the Huo family

645
00:37:23,070 --> 00:37:24,670
must pay the price.

646
00:37:25,880 --> 00:37:26,540
Otherwise,

647
00:37:26,840 --> 00:37:28,920
wouldn't anyone dare

648
00:37:29,480 --> 00:37:30,550
to challenge you?

649
00:37:36,880 --> 00:37:37,880
What do you want?

650
00:37:38,760 --> 00:37:39,840
The Elite Club—

651
00:37:40,440 --> 00:37:42,240
what kind of organization is it?

652
00:37:42,280 --> 00:37:42,940
Where is it?

653
00:37:43,320 --> 00:37:44,320
And how do I get in?

654
00:37:44,920 --> 00:37:45,480
What?

655
00:37:46,510 --> 00:37:48,510
You want to take down the Huo family?

656
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:50,650
You think you alone can do that?

657
00:37:52,360 --> 00:37:53,800
For the Murong family

658
00:37:54,070 --> 00:37:56,030
to attack the Huo family
for Qingyi right now

659
00:37:56,030 --> 00:37:57,290
would be unrealistic.

660
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:58,280
Moreover, in this family,

661
00:37:58,280 --> 00:38:00,110
the people who really care
if Qingyi lives or dies

662
00:38:00,110 --> 00:38:01,110
are very few.

663
00:38:01,480 --> 00:38:02,680
For you to take action

664
00:38:03,320 --> 00:38:04,710
would be unjustified,

665
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:06,940
and the cost would be too high.

666
00:38:07,230 --> 00:38:08,880
An outsider like me

667
00:38:08,880 --> 00:38:10,080
has no such concerns.

668
00:38:10,840 --> 00:38:11,640
Rest assured.

669
00:38:12,510 --> 00:38:13,970
Whether I succeed or fail,

670
00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:16,400
it has nothing to do with you.

671
00:38:23,670 --> 00:38:24,730
What are you after?

672
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:27,150
I'm after justice.

673
00:38:28,320 --> 00:38:29,320
Do you believe it?

674
00:38:34,550 --> 00:38:35,760
Justice?

675
00:38:41,920 --> 00:38:43,580
You overestimated yourself.

676
00:38:53,440 --> 00:38:55,150
I heard
when you came to the Murong family,

677
00:38:53,970 --> 00:38:55,920
♪ Sharper pain, deeper mark ♪

678
00:38:55,150 --> 00:38:56,230
it was quite a big scene.

679
00:38:55,940 --> 00:38:58,320
♪ Deeper care, greater torment ♪

680
00:38:59,590 --> 00:39:02,280
Rather than letting
your dowry and betrothal gifts

681
00:39:00,830 --> 00:39:02,590
♪ I won't give up on you ♪

682
00:39:02,610 --> 00:39:04,890
♪ Don't let go of me ♪

683
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:03,630
sit idle,

684
00:39:06,580 --> 00:39:09,400
♪ Let the ropes of fate ♪

685
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:09,420
you might as well put them
in the Huo family's treasury.

686
00:39:09,420 --> 00:39:12,380
♪ Bind you and me ♪

687
00:39:10,920 --> 00:39:12,360
Treasury?

688
00:39:13,170 --> 00:39:15,780
♪ Even if led to a precipice ♪

689
00:39:15,800 --> 00:39:18,690
♪ Together, we fall ♪
